This guide provides complete implementation steps to add User Action functionality to Anki-Android, similar to AnkiMobile.

## Overview

Users can define JavaScript functions (e.g., `revealNext()`) in their card templates and bind keys/gestures to trigger these functions. This is especially useful for:
- Using shared decks with custom keyboard shortcuts
- One-by-one cloze deletion reveals
